crawledImageUrls.text:
Falsely?s Flat Worlds is a collection of custom superflat worlds, constantly being updated. Currently, in Minecraft: Bedrock Edition it is not possible to create a custom flat world using the tools provided. However, I have created several flat worlds, with more being added all the time.
Falsely?s Flat Worlds currently has only 3 different flat worlds,
-Default (A higher version of the normal flat world)
-Sandstone (1 bedrock, 20 sandstone)
-Stone (1 becrock, 20 stone)
